Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, homeroom's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, guys, give it your all today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, but that was fast. How long has it\Nbeen since we became second-years?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're already so used to it\Nnow, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm so glad that we all\Ngot to be in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And we have Ms. Kyoko again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Especially for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.89,0:00:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The day they announced what class we'd be in,\Nthis one was so happy she was in tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a sweetheart, Onodera!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great that we even\Nhave the same seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's so great about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Ruri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're sitting near me, Ruri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it, you couldn't bear\Nto be separated from me–
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could you like, shut up for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.99,0:00:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only they'd assigned you\Nalone to another class,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we'd have nothing to complain about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seishiro, as usual, you're being perverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish that Kirisaki had been\Nassigned to another class, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:00:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The way I see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there are even more hot ladies\Nin this class, so I'm satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.55,0:01:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.26,0:01:11.02,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}June 3, On Duty: Raku Ichijo, Ruri Miyamoto{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.51,0:01:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who's on duty today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are some handouts leftover!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, isn't there anything you can\Ndo about that cohort of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's altogether too lacking in scruples.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.45,0:01:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's been like that as long as\NI can remember, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It must be hard on you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.91,0:01:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, although whoever that moron's\Ncrushing on should be pitied as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.83,0:01:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who that guy has a crush on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:52.02,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Support"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it isn't fair for you to know\Nwho I like and not vice-versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so who is it? This girl that you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, time for a quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the girl that I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said you got two\NValentine's chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo! Bingo! Right on the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For real? So I nailed it just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.04,0:02:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but which is the right answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd hate to give either one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One is a pure, cool beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,while the other is a perky, active\Nbeauty with dyed blond hair, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then is it Tanaka from Class D,\Nthe girl you sometimes talk to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo! Bingo! Right on the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.27,0:02:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-cchi's a fine gal, too.\NSo broad-minded and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. You're not even gonna\Ngive me a straight answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I'm dead serious, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that my love and respect\Nfor women is far too overpowering!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As a male high school student,\Nthat's something to be proud of!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You keep getting clobbered because\Nyou go around spewing stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some reason\Nwhy you can't tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:03:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But just like you have your\Nown way of conducting romance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, have my own way. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'll be fine carrying on\Nlike you always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.26,0:03:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's so entertaining\Nfor those of us observing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're making fun\Nof me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, in my case,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my target is an unattainable\Nflower, way beyond my reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops! Was that too big a hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, never mind about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck to you in your endeavors!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Hey, we're\Nnot done talking yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Seishiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be so kind as to\Ngive me an American-style hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. Is he like that year-round?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsugumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unattainable flower, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?\NDon't stare at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, has anyone ever said\Nyou were like a flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of drivel\Nis that, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, what would you do\Nif you fell in love with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Hey, hold up!\NWhat the hell are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For example, if he were\Nsomeone unattainable...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone you could never hope would\Nlove you back, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, my bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you haven't\Nexperienced first love yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to ask such an awkward question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd probably hide it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never tell a soul how I felt,\Nand never tell him either...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I would go on hiding it until\Nthe day that romance ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, but I have no experience\Nin any of that, so I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Needless to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that sounded like the opinion of\Na grownup with tons of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You girls really are incredible.\NI think I underestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not that it makes me\Nhappy to hear praise from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Tsugumi, if you really wanted to,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you could get\Nany guy that you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about it, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it's not Tsugumi, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, just remembering it\Nmakes my blood boil!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He always, always has that\Ncontemptuous attitude.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thoughtless jerks like him\Nannoy me more than anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's something he's never\Neven told his best friend, Ichijo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, there's someone I'm in love with!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder why he would tell me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:54.26,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Staff Room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go! Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to deliver\Nthe materials you requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Maiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, sorry to make you help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, since it's a request\Nfrom the one and only Kyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But in return, may I ask you to add\Nfive points to that English test?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall ever entering\Nsuch a secret contract with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll give you\Nthese leftover cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for your generosity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What else did you\Nwant me to fetch for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I can take care of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maiko, why don't I give you a heads-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See... I'm getting\Nmarried next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quitting to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving after this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! If that isn't\Nthe most splendid news!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Kyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Awww, hey, you're\Nembarrassing me! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, this makes me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:07:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our very own Kyoko, somehow snagging\Na husband just before she hits thirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly can't help\Nbreathing a sigh of relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you idiot! Lay off about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please invite me to\Nyour wedding, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want to catch your bouquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not mess with grownups.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, be safe on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know what? You're the only\Nmature one in the bunch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't forget to enjoy your youth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... today I have an important\Nannouncement to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting married, so I'll be\Nquitting after this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so you have a boyfriend, Kyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This month? But it's almost up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when are you getting married?\NWhat's your husband like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Ms. Kyoko's getting married!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a huge\Nannouncement, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So wonderful! But I think\Nwe're going to miss her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are we all gonna get\Nmarried, too, someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but you're\Nprobably set anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could probably make\Na great home with Onodera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you just taking\Nsomething like that for granted?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, this is totally unfair, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just give it up?\NWho you're crushing on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you, if you can guess, Raku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, is it Ms. Kyoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were tight, and you'll\Nmiss her when she's gone, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo, bingo! Right on the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko's a babe, and everybody loves her,\Nand we're all gonna miss her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You just lied, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Raku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It only happens once\Nin a blue moon, but I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since way back when... whenever\Nsomething happened to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I can always tell, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just once in a while, there are\Ntimes when I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey, this guy is lying\Nright now," you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When we were in sixth grade,\Nand your mom was in the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you always had the same\Nlook on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These childhood friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. I'm dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right after we started high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was like love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't going to\Ntell her how you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's getting married, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would only put her on the spot\Nif I confessed to her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Making sure I have no regrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that would just be\Nself-serving, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Raku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, this is a great\Nmemory in itself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to take this unrequited love,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and quietly put it away in a corner of my\Nheart as a bittersweet page of my youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfortunate, but I'm fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He has a point. It wouldn't do\N any good to confess now, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wouldn't do... any good, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that really true?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I were Shu,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and one day I had to say goodbye to someone\NI loved without even telling her how I felt...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wouldn't I have any regrets?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I were never going to\Nsee Onodera again,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if it were me, I'd want to\Ntell her how I felt... I think...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's say Onodera was getting\Nmarried to someone else–{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although just imagining that is like\Ninflicting horrible damage on my soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, I see it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Onodera was really in love with\Nthat person, and happy with him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wouldn't want to get in her way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Confess my love...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}True, I don't think I'd do it. But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? How unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For you to consult me about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember how I asked you yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"What if you fell in love\Nwith someone unattainable?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? That topic again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that person were to suddenly\Nsay he was getting married,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what would you do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you'd take one last\Nchance to tell him how you felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Married?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering about this yesterday,\Ntoo, but who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Young\NMistress is getting married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With somebody other than you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is just an example, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So? What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'd tell him\Nabout my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since he'd be getting married,\Nit would only cause him trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you do feel that way, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... Would you really\Nbe okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could you really live with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a matter of being\Nable to live with it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there's nothing else you can do,\Nthen there's nothing else you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can you sit there and be so\Nrealistic when you have no experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No... I'm not really!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just telling you\Nwhat I think I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just as I thought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's how you see it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really getting\Nmarried, Ms. Kyoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky you, getting married!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would it really be wrong to tell her\Nat a time like this how he feels?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is just so out of the blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so envious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ms. Kyoko,\Nwhat kind of person is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is he hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's just an ordinary guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when I'm with him,\NI guess it sets my mind at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat? He's ordinary?\NThat's so boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, can't you swoon a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's throw Kyoko a farewell party!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make it one to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's tomorrow, huh?\NMs. Kyoko's last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know how you're always\Nrooting for my romance to work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, although a lot of things you do\Ncan't really be called supportive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So now I'm gonna support you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna send Ms. Kyoko off\Nwithout saying anything to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll support your decision\Nnot to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's about all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So after Ms. Kyoko's gone, at least\Nlet me buy you dinner, just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks, Raku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The next day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ms. Kyoko's last day at our school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here, Raku Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only gonna say this\Nonce! Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, you asked me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I ever fell in love with someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and he was going to\Nmarry someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,would I tell him how I felt or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if I decided not to tell him,\Ncould I live with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why you would ask me such a thing, what it is\Nthat's eating away at you, I have no clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no clue, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, I believe my answer was\Nmisleading, so I'm going to correct myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because as someone you've\Nconsulted, I want to be responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That it wasn't a matter of\Nbeing able to live with it or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's just that you have\Nno choice but to live with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it doesn't mean\Nyou want to live with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You probably wouldn't\Nbe able to live with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about these things,\Nbut this emotion called love...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That must be how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, not that I have\Nany clue about such emotions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I've never fallen in love\Nwith anyone yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Tsugumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Was that Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What were you two talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just... about a theoretical romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On second thought, I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Raku! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty unusual. Are you ditching, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shu... I'm gonna say something just\Na little bit uncalled for now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I might be just as clueless\Nas you always say I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what other people are\Nfeeling unless they tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're doing\Nthe right thing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's the considerate,\Nmature call to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I also think that you should do\Nwhat it is that you really want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not gonna do anything,\NI'll support you for not doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also give you a push.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:18:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would you be\Ngiving me a push for, Raku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've just had my heart broken\Nin spectacular fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do when\Nthe romance is long over?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a single regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it even\Nhas to be me to spot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know what? You're the only\Nmature one in the bunch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't forget to enjoy your youth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could you give my back\None hell of a push?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's at the taxi stand\Nin front of the crosswalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...don't know if that was\Nthe right thing to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, that Four Eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go, ditching his duties?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Maiko! This is your job...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was that... Maiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you are enjoying your youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna make\Nan awesome man someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, Maiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did I meddle too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Raku...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Treat me to some octopus balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:21:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I do the right thing, I wonder?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks, Raku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got it out of my system.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it wasn't my style, I guess\Nit's not half bad, this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So? What are you gonna do, Raku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're not gonna\Ndo a thing about Onodera
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,after you just made me\Nconfess my feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No... that's actually, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know where you're coming from,\Nbut it's really complicated, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was only kidding. I think it's all good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For you to go at your own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But no regrets, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're ever on the verge of\Nmaking a choice that you'll regret,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll be the one to kick your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shu, you really are amazing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since I think if you told me\Nto confess to Onodera,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd have a really hard time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:21:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You vanished all of a sudden,\Nand I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, something came up...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen, Onodera.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.32,0:22:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to spring this on you\Nall of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go home with me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-But why? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.20,0:22:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No... I just kind of feel like it, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.38,0:22:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.76,0:22:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will, too...{\i0}
